  "body": "<!-- Please only use this template for submitting enhancement requests -->\r\n\r\n**What would you like to be added**:\r\nlet's say I run\r\n```\r\n$ kubectl wait deployement --for condition=available -l some=label  --timeout=60s\r\ndeployment_x condition is met\r\ndeployment_y condition is met\r\ntimed out waiting for condition\r\ntimed out waiting for condition\r\ntimed out waiting for condition\r\n```\r\nIf the deployment is comes up in time it tells me which deployment is up, but if it times out it doesn't tell me on which deployment/resource. Could it be\r\n\r\n```\r\ntimed out waiting for condition on deployment_a\r\ntimed out waiting for condition on deployment_b\r\ntimed out waiting for condition on deployment_c\r\n```\r\n**Why is this needed**:\r\nThat would make it easier to use, and the information provided is the same irregardless on whether the condition is met or not\r\n",
